  "text": "The normal/physiological range of the monitored biomarkers in saliva is the following: CRP: <3 ng/mL; cortisol: 0.15-0.65 μg/dL; IL-1β: 50-200 pg/mL; IL-6: 5-25 pg/mL [CITATION_1] . Baseline levels of all investigated biomarkers were in the physiological range in case of each participant, see Fig. 2 .",
